The paper deals with automatic video captioning, which involves computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep neural network structures, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with video processing, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves developing a model for automatic video captioning, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
